<title>UK: Smithkline names Poste chief tech officer.</title>
<headline>Smithkline names Poste chief tech officer.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Drugs and pharmaceuticals group Smithkline Beecham Pharmaceuticals on Wednesday named George Poste as its chief science and technology officer.</p>
<p>Poste, 52, will also retain his current job as chairman of the company's research and development division.</p>
<p>In the newly created position, Poste will be responsible for identifying and assessing new technologies for the company.</p>
<p>--London Newsroom +44 171 542 4366</p>
